          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1599558733295-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> chicken</strong> <strong>thighs</strong> to a baking tray and reserve the pan</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>chicken </strong>to a clean board and leave to cool slightly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
